Get level 1 (district) boundary polygon for Ivory Coast

Source: R/get_level_1.R
get_level_1.Rd

Get level 1 (district) boundary polygon for Ivory Coast

get_level_1(url = steer$url[steer$level == 1])

Arguments

url

URL of source map dataset for level 1 (district) boundary polygon for Ivory Coast. This is set to the URL specified in the internal steering file data included in the package which provides the URL from the Humanitarian Data Exchange.

Value

A SpatialPolygonsDataFrame class object for the level 1 (district) boundary polygon for Ivory Coast

Examples

# Get level 1 (district) boundary for Ivory Coast
get_level_1()
